      <item>
        <title>Court wizard competition</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[Shurian]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Heya!</p>
<p><em>A Magic Barrier protected you from…</em></p>
<p>Occupation. Ok.<br>
Redirection. Ok.<br>
Conversion. WAIT SOMEONE TRIED?<br>
<em>No message should appear. This was tried and CWs became too strong, too confirmable.</em></p>
<aside class="quote no-group" data-username="MissZero" data-post="1" data-topic="55218">
<div class="title">
<div class="quote-controls"></div>
<img alt="" width="20" height="20" src="https://www.ThroneOfLies.com/images/class-icons/observer-icon-256.jpg" class="avatar"> MissZero:</div>
<blockquote>
<p>Magic Door (3 charges): Hides the target for one night.</p>
</blockquote>
</aside>
<p>Explain this… Is it prevention? Word it in ToL terms. (Occupy/Redirect/Convert/Attack/Prevent)</p>
<p>Assuming its Prevention, 3 uses is too much, especially when you can use it on others. Prevention abilities are really powerful considered that no one can bypass (besides Frenzy). CW Ice Ward was 2 usages and it only can be cast on himself.<br>
<em>Consider toning it down to 2.</em></p>
          <p><a href="https://forum.throneoflies.com/t/court-wizard-competition/55218/19">Read full topic</a></p>
        ]]></description>
